resources.string:
This DICOM image viewer utilizes the OpenCV and dcm4che3 libraries.

This app is currently in public beta. If you experience any errors, please email me.

Author: Christopher Boyd
E-mail: help@simplydicom.com
Copyright 2013–2015
Please connect or insert external storage.
DICOMDIR (Media Storage Directory Storage) is not currently supported.
Compressed/JPEG images are not currently supported.
